&lt;h2 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQYfPSkfUBViHXQAjgDLAMsAcwB3HVABJgAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADVgAvADEAAA==&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;76634,5535,5542,76711,5666&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;31,41,80&#x27; data-armory-31-traits=&#x27;296,334,1675&#x27; data-armory-41-traits=&#x27;232,1502,226&#x27; data-armory-80-traits=&#x27;2391,2342,2335&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation&quot;&gt;Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The rotation for Evoker consists mainly of charging and casting both &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76585&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Conflagration as quickly and as many times as possible. Using any weapon skill 3 times will charge &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite, and using &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite 3 times will charge &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76585&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Conflagration.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your rotation consists of a simple opener and a &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement priority.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Try to always precast 2 stacks of &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite before the fight begins. This can be done by swapping to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77225&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Splash and using it twice as &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77225&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Splash can be used without any target selected. Remember to swap back to &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite once you have finished precasting.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opener:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Always be in &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5692&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dragon&#x27;s Tooth (Scepter Fire 2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5497&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Flamewall (Focus Fire 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5675&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phoenix (Scepter Fire 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76585&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Conflagration&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5678&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Shield (Focus Fire 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76711&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fox&#x27;s Fury&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5542&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Fire&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement Priority:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76585&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Conflagration&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5675&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Phoenix (Scepter Fire 3)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5497&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Flamewall (Focus Fire 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5692&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dragon&#x27;s Tooth (Scepter Fire 2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5678&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Shield (Focus Fire 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76711&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fox&#x27;s Fury&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5542&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Signet of Fire&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5666&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Glyph of Elementals&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Basically putting your professional skill first, weapon skills next, then utilities.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take note that casting &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76643&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Ignite too quickly after &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76585&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Conflagration may result in you cancelling &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76585&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Conflagration. However, this is a much more common problem with the fast pace of the &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2437&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Specialized Elements build, and is usually not a problem here apart from the opener.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build relies heavily on landing &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5497&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Flamewall (Focus Fire 4) to maintain &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;100947&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Fireworks uptime. Each tick of damage from the fire field generated by &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5497&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Flamewall (Focus Fire 4) resets &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;100947&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Fireworks duration, allowing you to easily maintain 100% updtime with just 1 skill and no cooldown management.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should also:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cast Off Cooldown:&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
